{"tid":2363150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西媒：皇馬仍在為C羅離開還債，場均入球剛好跌１球","createTime":"2021-01-12T04:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T15:26:19.000Z","uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6b5c2d4ea08b773496fa65664b253ec1b64302","tid":2363150,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"在齊達內第二次執教皇馬期間，皇馬有17%的比賽沒有進球，而在他第一次執教時，這一比例為9%，當時C羅在皇馬隊內。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F8c7fc022dbb3f4c612c69a8207b5018d.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F8c7fc022dbb3f4c612c69a8207b5018d.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=e698b6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  皇馬0-0戰平奧薩蘇納的比賽讓人沮喪，這也進一步暴露球隊中前場存在的弱點。<br />\n<br />\n  在拉莫斯和瓦拉內的帶領下，皇馬隊的防守已經類似於上賽季復賽後的防守，後防是皇馬贏得聯賽冠軍的基礎。在過去的9場比賽中僅僅丟了3個球就可以證明這一點。現在的問題在於攻破對方的球門。<br />\n<br />\n  在對陣奧薩蘇納的比賽中，皇馬只有8次射門，而且只有1次射正，這是阿森西奧的數據，他是當晚皇馬進攻體系中最犀利的。本澤馬有兩個越位進球被判無效，這位法國前鋒進入了新的進球荒。本澤馬已經連續三場比賽沒有進球，在對陣奧薩蘇納的比賽中，他顯得不在狀態，而主隊的防守接近完美。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Fc2e1b393448eee04ac390070f0c28d5b.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Fc2e1b393448eee04ac390070f0c28d5b.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=3b519283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  這是最近18場西甲比賽中，皇馬第三場沒有進球的比賽，這意味著每6場比賽中就有一場沒有進球。對於一支從2015-16賽季末到2017-18賽季初連續73場進球的球隊來說，這是一個令人擔憂的數據。當時皇馬的主帥就是齊達內，而且現在隊內有幾名隊員也參加了當時的連續進球。然而，那是一個不同的時代，C羅用他不可阻擋的進球，壯大了皇馬的數據。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F9aae354a9a1e8922b9e5f16e205cc973.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F9aae354a9a1e8922b9e5f16e205cc973.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=1ba9da08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  自從齊達內第二次執教以來，在86場交鋒中，皇馬已經有8場比賽沒有得分（17%）。在這位法國教練第一次執教皇馬期間，球隊在149場比賽中僅有9場（6%）沒有進球。兩個階段區別明顯的原因在於C羅的離開，他平均每個賽季進50球。<br />\n<br />\n  在過去的18場聯賽中，皇馬只進了30球（平均每場1.7球），這是繼2007年以來同期第二差表現，最差的是2018-19賽季的26球，那正是C羅離開皇馬後的第一個賽季。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  縱觀歷年的統計數據，C羅的影響對皇馬來說特別大。2017年，皇馬攻入156球；2018年（C羅6月離隊）他們攻入142球；2019年皇馬攻入100球；2020年皇馬只打入91球，這是自2005年以來最差的數字）。這意味著三年內皇馬進球數下降了40%。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  擔任皇馬主帥時，安切洛蒂談到C羅時說：&ldquo;在他上場的時候，我們的比賽就像是以1:0開始。這聽起來像個笑話，但這是事實。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F2d1067c473cabef1354f5f21045bb3ba.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F2d1067c473cabef1354f5f21045bb3ba.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b28b3375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  考慮到C羅離開後皇馬平均每場少進一球，安切洛蒂的話語顯然很正確。在C羅的帶領下，皇馬在503場比賽中攻入1385球，平均每場2.7球，而在後CR7時代，皇馬平均每場進1.8球（136場比賽241球）。皇馬的場均進球數差不多下降了1個，這正是C羅的進球數。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Fbaedc60f9fb4325735b75308a225bfdf.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Fbaedc60f9fb4325735b75308a225bfdf.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=60258fa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bd63993bbf74786839dbcfe514234612bd76c7b","tid":2363150,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/845/19859866845/19873848961_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F845%2F19859866845%2F19873848961_600x399.jpg&h=e22673eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38bb886c41270e0932cf463b34e47404e21513d4","tid":2363150,"uid":132322,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"收爺啦支那何求 日撚日c羅c羅"},{"pid":"f3fdb905e8d757b720497a5fc98a6f7786c844d9","tid":2363150,"uid":15084,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內文又係支那用語<br />\n做乜鳩"},{"pid":"1cf2511b1e44652cfb76a10489c62099b80c266f","tid":2363150,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"摩迪，拉膠都老啦<br />\n成隊都跌watt<br />\n有牙朗咪又係入少球"},{"pid":"a59dc7163196d7dbee50e2c5398fd1737266a713","tid":2363150,"uid":61015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"入黎係睇細路舉牌"},{"pid":"0f52527958ffd3c32e262c7e27369e25208f7b93","tid":2363150,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:21:42.000Z","msg":"巴利：團結團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58db2019bbc1872993269960db0acfba8932e3db","tid":2363150,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf2511b1e44652cfb76a10489c62099b80c266f","tid":2363150,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"摩迪，拉膠都老啦<br />\n成隊都跌watt<br />\n有牙朗咪又係入少球"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"十足十好似黃家駒咁<br />\n喺最高峰嗰個位走咗，可以一路吹奏到永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac8f4197fc0b6b1df55c8e583912d059c8200b","tid":2363150,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:28:28.000